highlights.text: Annika has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Stolt (feat. Lamin)” is the highest at #5.
“Reposado” by Benny Jamz and Gilli has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 430 days straight.
“Strategy (from the Netflix film KPop Demon Hunters)” by TWICE is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #171.
“NOKIA” by Drake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 103 spots at #90.
